window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tormented and racked with guilt over the brutal slaying of his wife and daughter, Charlie Parker, ex-cop with the NYPD, agrees to track down a missing girl. It is a search that will lead him into an abyss of evil. </p> <p>At the same time, he is warned by an old black woman in Louisiana that \"The Travelling Man\" is about to strike again. Multiple strands converge with a horrific confrontation in which hunter and hunted are intimately connected by guilt.</p>"; 
